@startuml
title Statechart diagram of the plane lifecycle

[*] --> Order
state Order
state "Arrival" as Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state "Out of Service" as OutOfService
state Historic

Order --> Arrival : plane acquired
Arrival --> Preparation : plane arrived
Preparation --> Operations : plane prepared and ready
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights
Maintenance --> Preparation : plane serviced and ready
Operations --> OutOfService : plane no longer available
Maintenance --> OutOfService : plane no longer available
OutOfService --> [*] : plane permanently withdrawn
Historic --> [*] : plane removed from operations
Order --> Historic : plane permanently withdrawn

@enduml
